sections.heading: to 9-20-18 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1992, ch. 57, § 56 repealed 9-20-1 to 9-20-18 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1988, ch. 101, §§ 1-16 and Laws 1990, ch. 32, §§ 1-2, relating to the Youth Authority, effective July 1, 1992. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1991 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.For present comparable provisions,see9-2A-1 NMSA 1978 et seq.
